-- Chrysler's U.S. sales down 6 percent in August
-- 
-- Tue Sep 4, 2007 4:07pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/04/us-chrysler-sales-us-idUSWNAS334920070904

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Chrysler LLC said on Tuesday its U.S. sales fell 6 percent in August as the automaker cut back on sales to daily rental companies. 

 Chrysler said it sold 168,203 vehicles in the United States last month, compared with 179,165 a year earlier. (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta )